videos.description: Demetrius Taylor sacks UNC QB Sam Howell then collects the fumble, taking it back 20 yards for the touchdown to give Appalachian State a 13-6 lead.

videos.headline: App State takes lead vs. UNC with scoop-and-score TD

videos.description: Appalachian State RB Darrynton Evans runs into the end zone untouched to give the Mountaineers a commanding lead over the Tar Heels.

videos.headline: Evans' 2nd TD gives App State 27-10 lead

videos.description: With under 10 seconds to play in the first half, UNC QB Sam Howell finds Michael Carter for an 11-yard touchdown, cutting the Tar Heel deficit to 10.

videos.headline: UNC scores TD just before halftime

videos.description: Sam Howell throws to the end zone and Carl Tucker hauls in the pass with just one hand to cap North Carolina's 15-play touchdown drive.
videos.headline: UNC's Tucker makes 1-handed TD grab
